      "type": "string",
      "content": "<div style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;'><h3 style='color: #2c3e50;'>Kettle Resistance Calculation</h3><p>Using energy and power relationships:</p><p style='background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #3498db;'><strong>P = E/t = 6.0×10⁵J / 300s = 2000W</strong><br><strong>R = V²/P = (240V)²/2000W = 28.8Ω</strong></p></div>"
